name: REFRACT - The GIFs - GIF-r27/48

This GIF is part of C5 along with GIF-r25, GIF-r26 and GIF-r28. First 11 collectors to complete C5 will be awarded with 1 edition of OBJKT#XXXXXX (to be revealed on Oct 7th).

First 11 collectors to complete the serie will be awarded with 1 edition of REFRACT -AV- (to be revealed on Oct 8th).
